## Extension rules

### Adding a new variant to {{module}} (policy pattern)
1. Create `src/{{module}}/policies/{{name}}.py` implementing `BasePolicy`
2. Implement the `evaluate(input, context) → Result` method
3. Register in `policies/registry.py`
4. Add tests covering the variant's edge cases
5. Write a spec in `docs/specs/{{name}}.md` if behavior is complex

### Adding a new module
1. Create `src/{{new_module}}/` with its own models and routes
2. Define the public contract in `docs/modular/modules.md`
3. Never import from other business modules — go through models
4. Add an ADR in `docs/plan/v1-mvp.md` explaining the new boundary
